title: Freebird font
content:
Hi, once again, I've been asked to do some work involving someone's branding, but I don't have any access to anyone who did the original work, so, please help me identify this font:   
   
 ![The logo in question](http://web.archive.org/web/20131108172428im_/http:/www.typophile.com/forums/messages/83/42057.gif)   
   
And, of course, I need to know it ASAP so I can finish the work by 5 CST.   
   
Thanks so much!
